{"tid":1283732,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"終於明白咩叫和而不同","createTime":"2019-07-04T01:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T04:12:35.000Z","uid":154406,"like":88,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a1ae673ee3741e25921c8897a7c6d5d8d828dec0","tid":1283732,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:46:52.000Z","msg":"父母係和理非黃絲，我係港獨/勇武派，71嗰晚睇直播大家都各自發表自己睇法，雖然父母未接受到衝擊垃圾會呢啲升級行為，但我同佢哋解釋我哋立場同埋原因嘅時候，佢哋就同我講：啊仔，如果你以後要出去幫手，我哋唔支持你，但點都唔會阻止你始終你已經大個，我哋老啦去唔到前面，記得一切小心。聽到真係好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ebb83209991c1db6c54003123f01023daa3a06e","tid":1283732,"uid":108337,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:53:30.000Z","msg":"要繼續宣掦依一個理念"},{"pid":"0f7a36120a14d373e65de2cbc2e1538c038e14cc","tid":1283732,"uid":154406,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:54:20.000Z","msg":"好慶幸屋企人都支持自己，見到出面啲離家出走post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4136291555617eb5854664bf657d34c3fa58f47","tid":1283732,"uid":165339,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:01:36.000Z","msg":"患難見真情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多弟兄姊妹都睇清楚屋企人"},{"pid":"49e809f5b538500764480233d8fd1f5039981634","tid":1283732,"uid":79373,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:19:19.000Z","msg":"同中間派和理非老豆示好咗 （自己仲係幾和理非不過理解點解有人會衝 因為出於絕望先咁 而佢同大部分和理非一樣覺得唔好衝立法會），佢都話總之我有衡量過 安全就得。同埋自己都盡量睇唔同角度唔同報道，cctvb到蘋果仲有外國媒體，起碼叫做睇得闊好過佢哋電視有乜就直接食落肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：有長期病患同本身抑鬱過，自己都特登搵咗friend幫手同FB做鍵盤戰士 po過緊急熱線叫人有事就出聲，真係唔想再有人了結自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ed32ba4d6a4ceb64d40e5cd8ac32f2d3f1cbad","tid":1283732,"uid":267869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:24:18.000Z","msg":"我身邊唔少父母子女 兄弟姐妹 夫婦面阻阻<br />\n樓主好幸運父母咁開明<br />\n<br />\n順便借位一用<br />\n<br />\n想幫人定想搵人傾下計嘅都入一入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1283766\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1283766</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"67d379c748ab15f2dd2e0315a75b7df252724513","tid":1283732,"uid":154406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:29:27.000Z","msg":"屋企人支持真係好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db152cf514bcfd8ba0ae7f7f34bb66254fd8bd6e","tid":1283732,"uid":217986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:41:52.000Z","msg":"社會做到和而不同可能先至係最好，因為可以互相監察。如果大家都活喺同温層應該拆天。<br />\n<br />\n我就係生活喺同温層。睇直播見到示威者俾人打，我屋企有位寶寶對住個電視嗌：「做咩淨係企喺度？屋企都未必捨得打憑咩俾佢哋打？」"},{"pid":"585c8a680d15b4dfeca5e0e5c887cc573c0fa74a","tid":1283732,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db152cf514bcfd8ba0ae7f7f34bb66254fd8bd6e","tid":1283732,"uid":217986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:41:52.000Z","msg":"社會做到和而不同可能先至係最好，因為可以互相監察。如果大家都活喺同温層應該拆天。<br />\n<br />\n我就係生活喺同温層。睇直播見到示威者俾人打，我屋企有位寶寶對住個電視嗌：「做咩淨係企喺度？屋企都未必捨得打憑咩俾佢哋打？」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:45:49.000Z","msg":"社會層面講就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇可能"},{"pid":"9a45efcc6570d21319cd8047637201ca20fa3397","tid":1283732,"uid":217986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"585c8a680d15b4dfeca5e0e5c887cc573c0fa74a","tid":1283732,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db152cf514bcfd8ba0ae7f7f34bb66254fd8bd6e","tid":1283732,"uid":217986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:41:52.000Z","msg":"社會